{"tid":806432,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"高質麥當勞打雜Group 招募鍾意傾計嘅你你你","createTime":"2018-09-04T16:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T12:28:16.000Z","uid":59837,"like":6,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d5594110693067796d13b9e94fbddae9da3c1c","tid":806432,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對上一次招收麥友係一年前<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣好多人混水摸魚扮自己友入嚟R水吹<br />\n<br />\n為咗確保返Group內麥友係高質嘅<br />\n<br />\n麻煩填一填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 畀你揸兩下喇最多<br />\n<br />\n基本上都係啲公司問題<br />\n<br />\n如果係麥友一定會答到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好以為我扮撚曬嘢 又要答問題先畀入<br />\n<br />\n因為Group裡面傾嘅嘢真係自己友先明白<br />\n<br />\n如果你睇唔明 我地都唔好意思喇是咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea14d07313d51642244e546472c4de15f2c18352","tid":806432,"uid":2419,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"乜撚野麥友呀 去剷薯條啦弱智仔"},{"pid":"86e6df63cef3c6b06f3efb04fb7cd5bc11221f77","tid":806432,"uid":113577,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾 全部都係垃圾"},{"pid":"9176efee20697855c3f413db47326e2c9a8868a1","tid":806432,"uid":198622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"717292b247c4ec043722c5a38d28f6d4c0eb216d","tid":806432,"uid":59837,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"ea14d07313d51642244e546472c4de15f2c18352","tid":806432,"uid":2419,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"乜撚野麥友呀 去剷薯條啦弱智仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:10:55.000Z","msg":"剷你老母啲老泥 正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/heh